{"id": "art-486", "label": "Art. 486", "title": "Art. 486: Cererea de recurs", "slug": "art-486", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 486: Cererea de recurs </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Cererea de recurs va cuprinde urm&#259;toarele men&#355;iuni:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1756720912\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1227\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1756720912\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)numele &#351;i prenumele, domiciliul sau\nre&#351;edin&#355;a p&#259;r&#355;ii în favoarea c&#259;reia se exercit&#259;\nrecursul, sau, dup&#259; caz, numele, prenumele &#351;i domiciliul\nreprezentantului conven&#355;ional, numele, prenumele &#351;i domiciliul\nprofesional al avocatului care formuleaz&#259; cererea ori, pentru persoanele\njuridice, denumirea &#351;i sediul lor, precum &#351;i numele &#351;i prenumele\nconsilierului juridic care întocme&#351;te cererea. Prezentele dispozi&#355;ii\nse aplic&#259; &#351;i în cazul în care recurentul locuie&#351;te în\nstr&#259;in&#259;tate;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>b)numele\n&#351;i prenumele, domiciliul sau re&#351;edin&#355;a ori, dup&#259; caz,\ndenumirea &#351;i sediul intimatului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)indicarea\nhot&#259;rârii care se atac&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>d)motivele\nde nelegalitate pe care se întemeiaz&#259; recursul &#351;i dezvoltarea lor\nsau, dup&#259; caz, men&#355;iunea c&#259; motivele vor fi depuse printr-un\nmemoriu separat;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2064602647\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1226\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2064602647\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)semn&#259;tura p&#259;r&#355;ii sau, dup&#259; caz, a\nmandatarului p&#259;r&#355;ii, a reprezentantului legal al p&#259;r&#355;ii sau\na consilierului juridic.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_315802826\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1225\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_315802826\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)La cererea de recurs se vor ata&#351;a dovada\nachit&#259;rii taxei de timbru, conform legii, precum &#351;i, dac&#259; este\ncazul, procura special&#259;, împuternicirea avoca&#355;ial&#259; sau\ndelega&#355;ia consilierului juridic.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1657848643\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1224\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1657848643\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Men&#355;iunile prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) lit. a)\n&#351;i c)-e), precum &#351;i cerin&#355;ele men&#355;ionate la alin. (2) sunt\nprev&#259;zute sub sanc&#355;iunea nulit&#259;&#355;ii. Dispozi&#355;iile art.\n82 alin. (1) &#351;i ale art. 87 alin. (2) r&#259;mân aplicabile.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}